  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      T cell depletion utilizing the CliniMACS device will allow more precise, specific and
      controlled graft engineering of peripheral blood stem cells from unrelated and partially
      matched related donors without an increase in relapse or graft rejection and grade III or IV
      acute graft versus host disease (GVHD).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
